imum at your guild's stage. The flurry/rampage drakes are rough on tanks and cleric mana. You need the DPS to be able to clear and recover, or else you will be in perma clearing mode. With the exception of Aary, Yvemm, and the triplets, the named are pretty easy. Clearing to them is the harder part.<br>
<br>
